        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: January 10, 2026</p>

        <p>At <strong>Metrowest Turnover Supply</strong>, we respect your privacy. This policy explains how we handle your information when you use our service.</p>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly to us, such as your name, delivery address, email, and phone number when you order a turnover kit.</p>

        <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>We use your data to process orders, manage deliveries, and communicate regarding your account. We do not sell your data to third parties.</p>

        <h2>3. Data Protection</h2>
        <p>In compliance with <strong>Massachusetts 201 CMR 17.00</strong>, we maintain security measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access.</p>

        <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You may contact us at any time to request a copy of your data or to ask for its deletion from our active records.</p>

